Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.20,0:19:24.96,Lyrics_A_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Unesená...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.34,0:19:36.61,Lyrics_A_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}...tichými vlnami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:36.61,Lyrics_A_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}saraware nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:53.09,Lyrics_A_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}sotto sotto
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.42,0:19:53.09,Lyrics_A_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Jemne, jemne...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:20:04.23,Lyrics_A_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}kietemo kamawanai kedo
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.85,0:20:04.23,Lyrics_A_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}Prestáva mi záležať na tom, či zmiznem.
