Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:31.01,Lyrics_A_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Ach... Strácajú svoje farby...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:31.01,Lyrics_A_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}aa iro wo otosu deshou
