Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.99,0:22:54.66,Lyrics_B_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,350)}Spať, túžiac znova sa stretnúť
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.66,0:22:59.83,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,350)}negai tsumugeru deshou ai no ito
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.66,0:22:59.83,Lyrics_B_SK,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,350)}a zamotať sa do vlákien lásky.
